Whether you’re an artist, storyteller, or creative enthusiast, this article provides a stunning visual and a long list of insightful tips to help you elevate your own prompt writing skills and unlock the full potential of your AI art.

Let the magic of prompts spark your next creative breakthrough!

## AI Image: Dragon in a City
![dragon](../../assets/posts/2024-10-22-dragons-to-life/jb-dragon-all.jpg)

## Prompt
` `code` `3d realism, Wide view, Full Length Shot(FLS), Natural light, A bustling city street scene where a person walks confidently beside two massive dragons, each towering over the surrounding buildings at 15-20 feet tall. The dragons, without any restraints, move gracefully but powerfully alongside the person, their scales shimmering under the bright city lights. The dragons' immense wings are folded, yet their sheer presence captures the attention of everyone around. Skyscrapers, busy shops, and speeding cars provide a modern backdrop, while crowds gather in awe, their phones raised to capture the surreal sight. The dragons exude an aura of ancient power, their fiery eyes glowing as they effortlessly navigate the crowded urban streets. People are stopping in their tracks, some whispering in disbelief, others taking selfies with the magnificent creatures in the background. The scene is filled with a mixture of excitement, fear, and fascination as these two colossal dragons walk freely, with their mighty tails gently sweeping the ground and their massive claws tapping on the pavement. The contrast between the majestic, mythical beasts and the bustling cityscape highlights the awe-inspiring moment of mythical creatures blending into the everyday world. --ar 9:16 --v 6.1 --quality 2` `code` `




